Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.17,0:06:43.34,main,Kashima,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.79,0:06:48.22,main,Kashima,0000,0000,0000,,You came by!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.22,0:06:49.23,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.23,0:06:50.84,sign_9812_142_Tsubame_Mizusaki,Autograph sign,0000,0000,0000,,Tsubame Mizusaki
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.07,0:06:50.84,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.84,0:06:54.37,main,Kashima,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! I watched your robot \Nanime at the culture festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.37,0:06:55.56,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I remember you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.63,0:07:00.60,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,And afterward, he sent a \Npassionate note of praise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.60,0:07:02.06,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,So that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.06,0:07:05.86,main,Kashima,0000,0000,0000,,Y'know, I watch a fair bit of anime, \Nand yours was great! I was moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.86,0:07:08.32,main,Kashima,0000,0000,0000,,The combination of realistic \Nrobot design principles
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.32,0:07:11.33,main,Kashima,0000,0000,0000,,with fantastical super robot action!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.33,0:07:14.28,main,Kashima,0000,0000,0000,,That's the kind of robot anime people \Nlike me have been waiting for!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.28,0:07:16.26,main,Kashima,0000,0000,0000,,It had the verisimilitude \Nthat makes you think
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.26,0:07:17.46,main,Kashima,0000,0000,0000,,the creators knew their stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.46,0:07:19.17,top,Kashima,0000,0000,0000,,And the monster seemed \Nlike it'd be right at home
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.30,0:07:20.74,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,He's actually praising the short.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.17,0:07:20.74,top,Kashima,0000,0000,0000,,in the Shibahama underground...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.74,0:07:23.27,top,Kashima,0000,0000,0000,,It's incredible you girls managed to \Npull that off while in high school!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.74,0:07:24.29,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I still feel like we've got too much to \Nwork on to accept it openly, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.27,0:07:24.71,top,Kashima,0000,0000,0000,,You're prodigies!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.15,0:07:27.55,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,This is better than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.05,0:07:33.52,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, seriously! I didn't think fruit \Nwould go well with ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.52,0:07:37.26,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Star fruit has a pretty mild flavor, \Nso there's pear juice in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.26,0:07:39.41,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You could even call it pear ramen instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.05,0:07:42.22,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,It goes to show that a dish can be good
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.22,0:07:45.45,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,even if the fruit used is barely noticeable,\N or bad if you notice it {\i1}too much{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.45,0:07:46.61,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Although part of it being good means
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.61,0:07:50.11,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,demonstrating what's unique \Nabout the fruit used.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.11,0:07:53.53,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,You never usually go that deep \Nwith your thoughts about food.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.53,0:07:54.49,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I think I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.49,0:07:57.22,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes you need to smother the taste \Nof the fruit for it to be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.38,0:07:59.83,main,Kashima,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.83,0:08:03.03,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably a little late to point this out, \Nbut this place is built on an angle, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.63,0:08:07.24,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Supposedly part of the reason \Nthe noodles are served without broth
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.24,0:08:08.83,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,is to keep it from spilling out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.38,0:08:13.43,main,Kashima,0000,0000,0000,,One pineapple dandan noodles, \Nand one dragon fruit dandan noodles!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.30,0:08:18.46,main,Kashima,0000,0000,0000,,Just between you and me, I've got \Nan incredible idea up my sleeve.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.02,0:08:20.24,main,Kashima,0000,0000,0000,,For an anime!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.24,0:08:23.39,main,Kashima,0000,0000,0000,,I just have no idea how I'd ever get it made.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.39,0:08:24.70,main,Kashima,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.70,0:08:25.98,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, sure, sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.98,0:08:28.58,main,Kashima,0000,0000,0000,,The protagonist is an \Nordinary guy who works at a
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.58,0:08:30.11,main,Kashima,0000,0000,0000,,dandan noodle place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.11,0:08:32.29,main,Kashima,0000,0000,0000,,But he has a secret identity...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.29,0:08:35.95,main,Kashima,0000,0000,0000,,He's actually an agent with the secret \Npolice force that protects world peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.02,0:08:40.41,main,Kashima,0000,0000,0000,,He uses his red pepper bombs \Nto fight off an alien invasion!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.41,0:08:41.66,main,Kashima,0000,0000,0000,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.66,0:08:44.66,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good to me. Let's use \Nthat for our new project.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.22,0:08:48.21,main,Other diners,0000,0000,0000,,The Yoshidas' place is gonna \Nbe closing this summer, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.21,0:08:50.21,main,Other diners,0000,0000,0000,,It's getting more and more lonely around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.13,0:08:55.25,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like our film club has a fan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.30,0:08:58.26,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot of deserted storefronts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:09:01.47,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Not a lot of customers outside of ski season.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:09:01.47,sign_12906_193_Don_t_play_in_th,Sticker sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(520,170,445,170)\fscy200}Don't play in the river by {\c&HC9C7C7&\3c&HF9FAF7&}yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.47,0:09:03.07,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,So what are we doing for our next project?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.07,0:09:05.19,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Are we gonna base it on one \Nof Asakusa's concepts again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.63,0:09:08.05,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Last time, we knew from the outset
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.05,0:09:10.61,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,it was going to be a robot \Nversus a giant monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.61,0:09:16.38,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,The first short had a setting from your \Nback catalog of ideas, right, Asakusa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.38,0:09:20.78,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,That was just because we needed \Nsomething fast, so we chose something simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.78,0:09:22.82,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,And the second time around, \Nwe used the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.82,0:09:24.86,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,What've you been doing there, Kanamori?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.86,0:09:25.66,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Making posts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.66,0:09:28.94,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Having fun playing around on\N social media. Must be nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.94,0:09:31.42,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing fun about social media!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.42,0:09:32.96,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you're already doing publicity?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.96,0:09:34.92,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Right. It's better to attract eyes beforehand
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.92,0:09:37.27,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,than trying to get attention \Naround the time of release.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.87,0:09:39.18,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Say butter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.65,0:09:40.72,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.72,0:09:43.14,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Is it all right if I post this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.14,0:09:44.73,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Well, sure, if it gets us attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.73,0:09:48.15,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I've been conscientious about \Nlikeness rights so far,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.57,0:09:50.02,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,but I'd like to set it up so that
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.02,0:09:53.85,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,only our followers can view the \Nposts with your face in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.85,0:09:55.59,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine. My parents \Nhandle my management anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.59,0:09:59.09,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,I really wish people would pay \Nattention to our projects and not me, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.09,0:10:01.16,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't worry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.82,0:10:04.49,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,The whole intent is to get people \Nto pay attention to the eizouken's output.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.49,0:10:05.94,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,We get them to develop an emotional attachment,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.51,0:10:10.19,sign_14494_219__Film__Merchandi,Twitter picture sign,0000,0000,0000,,(Film) {\c&H4FE6F0&\3c&H4354D3&}Merchandise in the Works
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.94,0:10:08.37,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,and stimulate their urge to spend money.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.37,0:10:09.17,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,We're selling merch?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.17,0:10:11.86,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,There's demand for merchandise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.19,0:10:16.17,sign_14630_224_What_kind_of_Eiz,Survey sign,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of Eizouken merchandise\N would you want?\N\N {\3c&HF3F4F6&}T-shirts\N Towels\N Pins\N Art books\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.86,0:10:13.54,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,That can be pricey to put together,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.54,0:10:15.30,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,but if we measure demand correctly, \Nwe can avoid risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.30,0:10:18.66,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,We can bust our humps working on a new DVD,\N and it might not sell at 1,000 yen...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.66,0:10:20.52,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,But all we need is to \Nstamp the club's logo on a
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.52,0:10:22.62,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,t-shirt and we can sell {\i1}that{\i0} for 2,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.62,0:10:24.55,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Even if Tsubame Mizusaki is \Nwhat got them in the doors,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.53,0:10:28.27,sign_14974_232__ACertainProgram,Post Sign,0000,0000,0000,,@ACertainProgramDsAccount\N {\c&HBBA270&}and 76 others liked your post.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.55,0:10:28.27,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,the number of people who are genuinely \Ninterested in our work is increasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:29.56,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Part of our goal here is to ensure
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:32.95,sign_15064_233_Film,Expansion map sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx200\fscy200\t(1,4680,\fscx1\fscy1)}Film
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.56,0:10:32.95,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,everyone who watched our last \Nproject picks this one up, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.95,0:10:35.46,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,The clips we post might go viral,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.46,0:10:37.36,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,giving people an idea of the \Nmaterial we're working on...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.36,0:10:40.01,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Having a large digital footprint can \Nhelp us in a variety of ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.01,0:10:41.73,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,You're a social media master.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.11,0:10:47.43,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! That's the Mizusaki bump!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.43,0:10:49.77,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,I never realized how important \Nadvertising could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.77,0:10:54.63,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Long ago, I bore witness to \Nthe death of a liquor store!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.15,0:11:01.82,sign_15828_242_Fukuya_Liquor_St,A,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,500)}Fukuya Liquor Store
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.15,0:11:01.82,sign_15828_243_Fukuya_Brewery,A,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Fukuya \NBrewery
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.15,0:11:05.75,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the liquor store you mentioned?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.75,0:11:06.71,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Seems busy enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.71,0:11:08.59,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,My relatives ran it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.59,0:11:11.05,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,It was a drinking spot with a good reputation,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.05,0:11:12.85,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,particularly among fans of Japanese sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.42,0:11:16.18,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,But the owner had a high standard for quality,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.18,0:11:18.66,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,which did him no favors with the locals
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.66,0:11:21.51,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,who just wanted to get hammered at a low price.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.51,0:11:23.37,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,That's a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.37,0:11:24.73,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,The construction of the monorail
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.73,0:11:27.58,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,meant that the street trolleys \Nwere done away with,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.58,0:11:29.36,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,and since people drove more,\Nthey couldn't drink as much,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.58,0:11:31.64,sign_16486_253_Missing,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-2.07\pos(227,155)\fad(1,750)}Fukuya Liquor Store
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.36,0:11:30.83,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,leading to even fewer customers...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.83,0:11:33.05,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Which meant less of an emphasis on brewing,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.64,0:11:34.02,sign_16583_254_Missing,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(366,157)\fsp1\fad(500,500)}Fukuya Liquor Store
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.05,0:11:36.17,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,and by the time my uncle was running it,\N they called it a general store.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.25,0:11:39.30,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bit more run down, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.43,0:11:42.59,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,An exemplary general store!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.06,0:11:44.59,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,It's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.59,0:11:45.65,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.50,0:11:48.81,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Minimori!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.23,0:11:57.64,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,What a hard worker.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.64,0:12:00.63,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I heard pensions weren't \Nenough to get by anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.63,0:12:03.34,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,so I was trying to earn money \Napart from just my allowance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.99,0:12:08.62,main,Auntie,0000,0000,0000,,This place looks a lot cleaner! Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.62,0:12:10.08,main,Auntie,0000,0000,0000,,Here's a little tip.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.08,0:12:11.58,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.94,0:12:13.95,main,Auntie,0000,0000,0000,,You should really wait until \Nyou're home to open it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.95,0:12:15.54,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,There's extra.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.54,0:12:18.26,main,Auntie,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to add something special \Nsince you come by every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.86,0:12:21.55,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna clean some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.05,0:12:26.99,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Old...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.05,0:12:30.02,sign_17864_275_Closed,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Closed
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.97,0:12:33.02,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.02,0:12:35.61,main,Auntie,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my goodness! You're covered in snow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.61,0:12:38.34,main,Auntie,0000,0000,0000,,Did you walk here? That couldn't have been easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.34,0:12:39.98,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to open the store?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:43.26,main,Auntie,0000,0000,0000,,No one's gonna be out in this snowstorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.26,0:12:45.53,main,Auntie,0000,0000,0000,,Even the convenience stores are closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.18,0:12:49.63,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,But people need to buy stuff all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.63,0:12:52.04,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,If we open up right now, we'll be\N the only place making money.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.04,0:12:54.61,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I saw footsteps in front \Nof the store, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.77,0:12:57.74,main,Auntie,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we'll need that snow shoveled, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.74,0:12:58.49,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.31,0:13:02.76,main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,You ever notice the kinds of things she does?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.76,0:13:05.37,main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,She started shoveling in front of \Nthe vending machine, for instance...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.37,0:13:08.43,main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,That means we can start making money \Nas soon as that bit of snow is cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.81,0:13:10.93,main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,Hot drinks sell at times like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.38,0:13:12.77,main,Auntie,0000,0000,0000,,She really is thoughtful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.77,0:13:14.85,main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,She's always got her little eyes open.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.85,0:13:16.82,main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know she has trouble with math?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.82,0:13:19.22,main,Auntie,0000,0000,0000,,When she's got such a mind for business?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.22,0:13:20.61,main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,Funny, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.61,0:13:23.22,main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,Thing is, you can be a math wiz, but if\N you don't have a head for business—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.22,0:13:25.70,main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,the way I don't—it won't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:29.45,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,It's all clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.45,0:13:30.45,main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,Attagirl!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.94,0:13:33.07,main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,No tip this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.07,0:13:35.87,main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,Instead, you can have these. Sell what\N you've got, and make some money.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.30,0:13:40.63,main,Customer,0000,0000,0000,,Man, it's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.63,0:13:41.51,main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.51,0:13:42.77,main,Customer,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any gloves?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.77,0:13:46.59,main,Customer,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking about shoveling, \Nbut all I had were thin rubber ones...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.45,0:13:49.22,main,Customer,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, not like those.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.22,0:13:52.15,main,Customer,0000,0000,0000,,I was looking for something nice and thick\N that the snow couldn't soak through.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.15,0:13:54.58,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,If you put your rubber gloves on top of these...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.58,0:13:56.23,main,Customer,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.23,0:13:58.19,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.89,0:14:00.90,main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,Already making a sale!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.90,0:14:02.89,main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,And you sold a single pair of \Nworking gloves for 100 yen,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.89,0:14:04.89,main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,when they're usually a dozen for 300!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.89,0:14:06.44,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Individual sales stack up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.94,0:14:13.06,main,Truckers,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're open!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.06,0:14:13.97,main,Granpda,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.97,0:14:16.67,main,Truckers,0000,0000,0000,,Hey mister, is the vacant \Nlot across from you open?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.67,0:14:18.22,main,Truckers,0000,0000,0000,,We were hoping to park there for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.22,0:14:19.79,main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,Not a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.79,0:14:21.13,main,Trucker,0000,0000,0000,,Is it all right if we eat in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.13,0:14:22.00,main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,Make yourself at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.36,0:14:23.96,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,We have instant noodles.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.36,0:14:23.96,sign_20676_323_Soy_Ramen,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Soy Ramen
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.96,0:14:25.95,main,Trucker,0000,0000,0000,,That's perfect! You got hot water?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.95,0:14:26.61,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,We do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.61,0:14:28.47,main,Trucker,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, he says it's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.47,0:14:31.34,sign_20823_327_20_yen,Kettles sign,0000,0000,0000,,20 yen
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.05,0:14:31.34,main,Truckers,0000,0000,0000,,Man, this is just what I needed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.67,0:14:33.85,main,Truckers,0000,0000,0000,,Can feel myself warming up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.33,0:14:34.75,main,Truckers,0000,0000,0000,,This is good stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.19,0:14:41.29,main,Trucker,0000,0000,0000,,We set out to help folks stuck in \Nthe snow, but everywhere was closed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.85,0:14:50.82,sign_21024_331_Missing,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-3.9\fax-0.12\move(240,45,430,45)}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.29,0:14:45.82,main,Trucker,0000,0000,0000,,Even the convenience store, and we \Nwere starving! I thought we might be done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.35,0:14:48.93,main,Trucker,0000,0000,0000,,I never knew a place like this \Nwas just across the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.93,0:14:50.82,main,Trucker,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming here every week from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.82,0:14:55.16,main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate the thought, but we're\N actually closing this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.16,0:14:56.62,main,Trucker,0000,0000,0000,,What, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.62,0:14:58.96,main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,We've been in the red for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.96,0:15:00.63,main,Trucker,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not the best location.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.63,0:15:03.57,main,Trucker,0000,0000,0000,,You're kinda out of the way and hard to notice,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.57,0:15:05.65,main,Trucker,0000,0000,0000,,plus there's a convenience \Nstore right over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.65,0:15:08.30,main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,It was better when the trains \Nwere still running, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.30,0:15:10.78,main,Trucker,0000,0000,0000,,They never finished that damn monorail, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.78,0:15:13.86,main,Trucker,0000,0000,0000,,How about you only open up on snowy days?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.86,0:15:15.42,main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think we could manage that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.42,0:15:18.50,main,Trucker,0000,0000,0000,,Man, if I had known sooner, \NI would've told all my pals!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.50,0:15:21.46,main,Trucker,0000,0000,0000,,You let our nasty old cars park outside,\N and you let people stay and eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.46,0:15:22.82,main,Trucker,0000,0000,0000,,This is a great place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.82,0:15:25.81,main,Trucker,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess since everyone going into \Nthe mountains uses the other road...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.37,0:15:30.03,main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.03,0:15:32.41,main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,...well, I guess not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.38,0:15:35.91,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You're closing even though \Nyou could get customers?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.85,0:15:40.91,main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,You need money to even keep a store open.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.91,0:15:45.22,main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,Heating, repairs, taxes, insurance...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.22,0:15:48.31,main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,The money to buy stock and have it brought in,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.31,0:15:50.92,main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,which goes to waste if anything doesn't sell...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.92,0:15:53.63,main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,And since we're out of the way, \Ncustomers just don't come by.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.22,0:15:58.85,main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,We've been spending all kinds of money, \Nand only surviving off of what was left.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.85,0:16:02.56,main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,You can't keep a business open with \Nonly the odd customer here and there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.31,0:16:05.14,main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,260)}No one's gonna come to a store...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.14,0:16:07.41,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(783,1)}...that nobody knows about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.45,0:16:11.44,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in focusing entirely \Non the quality of your product.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.92,0:16:13.66,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You need the right methods\Nand products at the right time,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.66,0:16:15.02,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,and you need advertising!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.02,0:16:17.57,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,If you think a good product is all \Nit takes to attract customers,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.57,0:16:18.83,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,you're dreaming!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.83,0:16:21.01,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do business without promotion,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.01,0:16:23.69,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,but without a product, \Nyou can't even get started!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.69,0:16:24.88,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,High standards aren't enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.88,0:16:27.89,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You also need to think about how \Nto loosen people's purse strings!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.89,0:16:29.67,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll make sure people \Nhear about what we make.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.67,0:16:31.11,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.03,0:16:34.85,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Last time, we used the Shibahama High campus,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.85,0:16:38.75,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,but this time, I'm thinking of basing \Nthe story in the town itself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.18,0:16:42.27,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,The bizarre terrain and constructions!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.27,0:16:44.46,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,A town that's like a watery labyrinth!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.46,0:16:47.33,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Shibahama is a town where you can \Nsee the remains of trial and error
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.33,0:16:49.15,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,throughout history, which makes it fascinating!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.15,0:16:52.82,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's a treasure chest of concepts! \NA 4D pocket dimension full of ideas!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.49,0:16:55.92,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,The town comes under attack one day!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.49,0:16:56.32,sign_24300_380_Missing__Missing,SFX,0000,0000,0000,,Zoom  Screech  Pow
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.92,0:16:57.49,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Their enemies are UFOs!
