Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.33,0:17:20.78,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,That's kinda cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.78,0:17:22.00,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,If we used the town for the setting,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.00,0:17:23.87,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,do you think people who live \Nhere will be more invested?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.87,0:17:26.19,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Can you wrap this up in 30 minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.19,0:17:27.85,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still figuring out the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.85,0:17:30.94,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,But regardless, we've got the premise \Nand setting for our next project figured out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.42,0:17:33.23,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,The eizouken's next project...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.23,0:17:35.69,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,is the Shibahama-UFO Battle!
