Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.73,0:18:17.73,main,D,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I heard that the student \Ncouncil started taking the rent I'm paying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.73,0:18:18.90,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, are we gonna be okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.90,0:18:20.95,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,What about the budget for the new project?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.95,0:18:24.13,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I just finalized a deal where the \NShibahama Chamber of Commerce
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.13,0:18:26.61,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,has agreed to fully finance the short.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.09,0:18:28.39,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,That's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.39,0:18:30.96,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you do it?! Was it thuggery?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.96,0:18:34.53,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kashima from the \Ndandan noodle shop lent his support.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.53,0:18:37.34,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,He's the president of the \NYoung Person's Association,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.34,0:18:41.26,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,and has been working on local \Nrevitalization projects for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.26,0:18:44.76,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I pitched the idea of a local \Npromotional anime, and they ate it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.26,0:18:44.76,sign_26884_449_Revitalizing_the,Whiteboard sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx120}Revitalizing the town {\c&HC1949A&}through {\c&H6A58C0&}animation{\c&HA3B88A&}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.26,0:18:44.76,sign_26884_449_Revitalizing_the,Whiteboard sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H959693&\fs8\pos(203,62)}• Tsubame Mizusaki will be involved\N • Entertain kids\N • Make it an event for the\N shopping district\N • Voice acting auditions\N{\c&H9779CC&}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.26,0:18:44.76,sign_26884_451_Fun_,New Poster sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-83.66\pos(447,102)\fscx180}Fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.76,0:18:46.74,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know Kashimacchy \Nwas into stuff like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.74,0:18:48.23,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,That's a crazy coincidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.23,0:18:51.90,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Kanamori, did you take us to \Nhis shop knowing this would happen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.90,0:18:57.11,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,All I did was help the two of you brainstorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.97,0:19:00.11,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,How is the story progressing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.11,0:19:01.85,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.35,0:19:04.88,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Mizusaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.88,0:19:05.91,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.50,0:19:11.03,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,She said she was working on a \Nnew model of Adamski saucer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.70,0:19:23.67,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see the storyboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.67,0:19:25.09,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Here's what I've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.64,0:19:28.57,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,This is all the direction \Nyou've given so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.23,0:19:31.22,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,You're overdoing it again, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.22,0:19:33.77,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Quit making extra animation work!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.26,0:19:36.04,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,It's already done! It'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.04,0:19:37.17,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Get down here, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.17,0:19:39.74,top,M,0000,0000,0000,,Might need a few adjustments, \Nor there could be—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.15,0:19:40.32,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Your little R&D project is canceled!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.32,0:19:42.73,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,It's just gonna get shot down \Nby this thing, anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.44,0:19:59.61,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the beam? What about the laser?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.61,0:20:01.14,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Energy weapons weren't originally supposed to be
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.14,0:20:02.53,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,in the visible spectrum, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.53,0:20:05.86,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,There's no type of light that just \Nzips through the atmosphere like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.86,0:20:09.31,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, there are different \Ntypes of directed energy weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.31,0:20:11.74,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's not all about lasers, y'know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.74,0:20:14.61,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,And even with lasers, they fire \Nlight at speeds the eye can't track,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.61,0:20:16.17,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,for only a fraction of a second,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.17,0:20:18.38,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,so it's not gonna look like \Nthe spotlight at a concert!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.38,0:20:20.49,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it was plasma, there'd be—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.53,0:20:22.11,top,K,0000,0000,0000,,You might know what you're saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.11,0:20:24.60,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,but normal people are\N going to be watching this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.60,0:20:25.82,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,D-Does it not work?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.75,0:20:27.73,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the—?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.22,0:20:29.54,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,What's this sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.61,0:20:33.85,main,D,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really get all the specifics,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.85,0:20:36.25,main,D,0000,0000,0000,,but I was imagining this for after the gun fires.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.54,0:20:39.98,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,You can hear fans and chains come in contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.98,0:20:41.93,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,And the rumble is the excitation \Nof an electric generator.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.93,0:20:44.53,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,This really fits the way \Nthe concept is conceived.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.53,0:20:47.51,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Save the protracted analysis for \Nthe next time we're getting ramen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.51,0:20:49.37,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it rattling a bit too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.37,0:20:50.77,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.77,0:20:52.30,main,D,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.30,0:20:54.26,main,D,0000,0000,0000,,This is how it's supposed to sound!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.26,0:20:56.05,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it, the sound is fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.05,0:20:59.07,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,But I was thinking something more like...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.49,0:21:16.80,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.80,0:21:18.22,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,And what does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.22,0:21:21.26,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,For the, "Pow!" part, it doesn't \Nneed any additional sound!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.30,0:21:24.34,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,And then no sound after that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.34,0:21:27.26,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so that's how you want it performed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.68,0:21:28.89,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Performed?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.33,0:21:32.29,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think of her take, Doumeki?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.29,0:21:34.33,main,D,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not opposed to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.33,0:21:37.10,italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,That's it... It's a performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.71,0:21:41.15,italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,The reason the plane's interior \Nwas pitch black...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.23,0:21:45.61,italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,It was to demonstrate how \Nvast and bright the sky was.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.24,0:21:48.82,italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Everything I've been doing \Nso far has been a performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.82,0:21:50.83,italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,It's been that all along...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.83,0:21:52.81,italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,To depict a vast, unknown world that you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.81,0:21:54.55,italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,could never grasp from the \Nglimpse of a single image...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.33,0:21:57.98,italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,I've been choosing what \Nto draw, and how, all along!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.98,0:22:02.15,italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,But I never realized that what \NI was doing was a performance!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.15,0:22:04.30,italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what bitter fruit my ignorance has borne!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.30,0:22:06.47,italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,Construction and consistency!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.01,0:22:08.89,italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,The glory that these factors give rise to!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.74,0:22:13.22,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Performance will be how I demonstrate \Nthe greatness of the world I've imagined!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.58,0:22:17.59,italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,And with that being the case, \NI must consider the issue further!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.63,0:22:20.23,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't drawing no lasers!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.73,0:22:24.19,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Down, girl. Let me explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.73,0:22:28.97,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Drawing a cannon that doesn't \Nemit a beam is important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.05,0:22:32.52,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Using this cut, you can make it obvious \Nthat the gun is what shot down
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.52,0:22:34.20,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,the UFO from their relative positions.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.37,0:22:37.67,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not enough to resolve the issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.61,0:22:40.87,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,You think there'll be dissonance \Nif there's no beam or bullets involved?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.87,0:22:42.05,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.05,0:22:43.38,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, people...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.38,0:22:46.57,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,"This is a directed energy weapon \Nthat doesn't project a ray!"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.57,0:22:50.41,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,We have to make sure the \Nscene conveys that clearly!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.41,0:22:53.14,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, we add a cut that \Nmakes it obvious something was fired,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.14,0:22:54.22,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,even if there was no beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.22,0:22:57.77,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,We beef that sucker up with visual cues \Nfor a massive energy expenditure,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.77,0:23:00.23,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,whether it was visible or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.23,0:23:02.81,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,And we need sound, Doumeki!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.77,0:23:08.45,main,K,0000,0000,0000,,I get how you want the scene performed, \Nbut what are the UFOs here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.45,0:23:11.20,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, yeah. Who's in them?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.20,0:23:13.27,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,That... I am not sure about, yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.27,0:23:17.27,main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, why was the town \Nso heavily armed, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.27,0:23:19.11,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna think that up later, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.11,0:23:23.58,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,For now, our goal is to prepare for Comet A...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.18,0:23:26.66,main,A,0000,0000,0000,,By creating the greatest world!
